---
import "../styles/global.css";
import HeaderNavBar from "../components/headerNavBar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/footer.astro";
import { getImage } from "astro:assets";
import myBackground from "../../src/images/Background.jpg"

const optimizedBackground = await getImage({src: myBackground, format: 'avif', alt:"",  height:1920, width:1080});
import Logo from "../images/horizontal.svg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div style="
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
	background:rgba(68, 170, 43, 0.363);
">
  <div
    style="position: sticky;top:0;display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column; background:white;"
  >
    <div
      style="display:flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"
    >
      <Logo style="padding: 15px;" />
    </div>
    <div
      style="flex: 1;flex-direction: row;display: flex;justify-content: center;"
    >
      <button
        style="align-self: end;"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg xl:btn-xl"
        >About</button
      >
      <button
        style="align-self: end;"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg xl:btn-xl"
        >Fees</button
      >
      <button
        style="align-self: end;"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg xl:btn-xl"
        >FAQ</button
      >
      <button
        style="align-self: end;"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg xl:btn-xl"
        >Services</button
      >
      <button
        style="align-self: end;"
        class="btn btn-ghost btn-xs sm:btn-sm md:btn-md lg:btn-lg xl:btn-xl"
        >Contact</button
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style={`flex: 1;justify-items: center;background-image: url(${optimizedBackground.src});background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover;background-position-y: center;`}>
    <div
      style="width:70%;margin: auto;padding: 20px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;gap: 20px; margin-top:40px; margin-bottom: 40px;"
    >
      <div
        style="color: white;font-size: 2em;font-weight: bold;padding: 20px;text-shadow: 0px 0px 6px black;"
      >
        Welcome
      </div>
      <div style="color: white;font-size: 1.5em;text-shadow: 0px 0px 6px black;padding: 20px;">
        Give yourself permission to start your healing journey
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="flex: 1;justify-items: center;">
    <div
      style="width:70%;margin: auto;padding: 20px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;gap: 20px; margin-top:40px; margin-bottom: 40px;"
    >
    <div style="text-shadow: 0px 0px 6px black;">
      If you are thinking of setting out on your therapy journey, congrats! It
      is an investment that will be so worthwhile. We all run into road
      blocks, challenging times, unforeseen circumstances and painful times,
      all of which can take a toll on us! Through the therapy process the goal
      is that you will be able to recover and protect your mental peace and
      well-being, gain tools to set you on a firm foundation for current or
      future challenges, and uncover your strengths. Learn to become more
      aware and in tune with your needs, how your experiences have shaped you
      and what changes you want to make in your life.
    </div>
    <div style="text-shadow: 0px 0px 6px black;">
      Therapy is not a passive process. It requires time, commitment and a
      willingness to change. We will journey together to help you discover
      your best path forward and feel more empowered in your life.
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>



  <div style="flex: 1;justify-items: center;">
    <div
      style="margin: auto;padding: 20px;display: flex;flex-direction: row;gap: 20px; margin-top:40px; margin-bottom: 40px;flex-wrap: wrap;"
    >
    <div
      style="margin: auto;padding: 20px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;gap: 20px; margin-top:40px"
    >
      <!-- <Image src={myImportedImage} alt="Therapist" style="border-radius: 10px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);" /> -->
    </div>
	<div
	style="margin: auto;padding: 20px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;gap: 20px; margin-top:40px"
  >
	<div
	  style="font-size: 2em;font-weight: bold;padding: 20px;text-align: center"
	>
	  Methodology
	</div>
	<ul>
	  <li>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</li>
	  <li>Dialectical Behavioral Therapy (DBT)</li>
	  <li>Mindfulness</li>
	  <li>Narrative Therapy</li>
	  <li>Exposure Therapy</li>
	  <li>Psychodynamic Therapy</li>
	  <li>Motivational Interviewing</li>
	  <li>Humanistic Therapy</li>
	  <li>Person-Centered Therapy</li>
	  <li>Acceptance and Commitment Therapy (ACT)</li>
	</ul>
  </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
<Footer style="flex: 1;background: rgb(132, 0, 255);min-height: 10vh;" />
